sign~
@@W*** Welcome to the Academy of Adventure! ***@@N

This academy will teach you everything you need to survive in the world.
Read the @@Wsigns@@N in each room carefully -- they contain vital lessons.

To read a sign, type '@@yLOOK SIGN@@N'.

When you are ready, go @@yNORTH@@N to begin your training.

~
S
