room.  Follow the signs to come back here.

  @@yNORTH@@N, @@ySOUTH@@N, @@yEAST@@N, @@yUP@@N, and @@yDOWN@@N lead to practice alcoves.
  @@yWEST@@N takes you back to the lesson corridor.

After you have tried all six directions, go @@yWEST@@N to continue.

~
