sign~
@@WKeys and Locked Doors@@N

The door to the @@yNORTH@@N is locked!  You need a key to open it.

Pick up the key on the floor by typing '@@yGET KEY@@N'.
Then type '@@yUNLOCK NORTH@@N' to unlock the door.
Then type '@@yOPEN NORTH@@N' to open it.
Finally, go @@yNORTH@@N to continue.

~
