sign~
@@WLesson III: Configuration@@N

You can customize how the game looks and behaves with these commands:

  @@yCONFIG@@N          -- See your current settings
  @@yCONFIG +COLOUR@@N  -- Turn on color (makes things pretty!)
  @@yCONFIG +AUTOEXIT@@N -- Automatically show exits in each room
  @@yCOLOUR@@N          -- See available colour themes
  @@yPROMPT ALL@@N      -- Show HP, mana, and movement in your prompt

Try typing '@@yCONFIG@@N' now to see your settings.

When ready, go @@yEAST@@N.

~
S
