sign~
@@WLesson IV: Communication@@N

You can talk to other players using channels:

  @@yGOSSIP <message>@@N  -- Talk to everyone on the gossip channel
  @@yNEWBIE <message>@@N  -- Ask questions on the newbie channel
  @@yQUESTION <msg>@@N    -- Ask a question publicly
  @@yTELL <name> <msg>@@N -- Send a private message to someone
  @@yPRAY <message>@@N    -- Send a message to the immortals (staff)
  @@ySAY <message>@@N     -- Speak to everyone in your room

To see available channels, type '@@yCHANNELS@@N'.
To turn a channel on or off: '@@yCHAN +GOSSIP@@N' or '@@yCHAN -GOSSIP@@N'.

Other channels include: @@yAUCTION@@N, @@ySHOUT@@N, @@yYELL@@N, @@yRACE@@N, and @@yCLAN@@N.

When ready, go @@ySOUTH@@N.

~
S
