sign~
@@WLesson VI: Items and Equipment (Part 2)@@N

To use equipment, you wear or wield it:

  @@yWEAR <item>@@N      -- Wear a piece of armor
  @@yWIELD <item>@@N     -- Wield a weapon in your hand
  @@yREMOVE <item>@@N    -- Stop using a piece of equipment
  @@yEQUIPMENT@@N (or @@yEQ@@N) -- See what you are currently wearing
  @@yWEAR ALL@@N         -- Wear everything you can from your inventory

Pick up the @@ysword@@N and @@ybuckler@@N from the table:

  Type '@@yGET ALL@@N', then '@@yWIELD SWORD@@N', then '@@yWEAR BUCKLER@@N'.
  Or just '@@yWEAR ALL@@N' after picking things up.

Check your equipment with '@@yEQUIPMENT@@N'.

When ready, go @@yNORTH@@N.

~
S
