sign~
@@WThe Trial Hall@@N

Beyond each passage is a creature or training target with equipment.
Kill each one and take their gear!

After killing a monster:

  @@yGET ALL CORPSE@@N    -- Loot all items from the corpse
  @@yWEAR ALL@@N          -- Put on your new equipment
  @@ySACRIFICE CORPSE@@N  -- Offer the corpse to the gods for a reward

Between fights, you may need to recover:

  @@yREST@@N   -- Sit down and recover HP slowly
  @@ySLEEP@@N  -- Fall asleep and recover HP quickly (but less aware!)
  @@yWAKE@@N   -- Wake up or stand up when done resting

Kill all seven targets and collect their gear, then go @@yDOWN@@N.

~
S
