sign~
@@WLesson X: Rules and Etiquette@@N

@@RRULE I:@@N   No swearing or offensive language on public channels.
@@RRULE II:@@N  No player killing without consent.  Respect the PK system.
@@RRULE III:@@N No kill-stealing -- do not attack monsters others are fighting.
@@RRULE IV:@@N  Respect the Immortals (staff).  They volunteer their time.
@@RRULE V:@@N   Ask questions!  Use '@@yNEWBIE@@N' or '@@yPRAY@@N' channels for help.

@@WUseful commands:@@N
  @@yBUG <message>@@N   -- Report a bug you found
  @@yIDEA <message>@@N  -- Suggest an idea for the game
  @@yTYPO <message>@@N  -- Report a typo
  @@yHELP@@N            -- Browse the help system
  @@yHELP <topic>@@N    -- Get help on a specific topic

When ready, go @@ySOUTH@@N to graduate!

~
S
